[
  {
    "bookname": "Malachi",
    "chapter": "3",
    "text": "\u201cI am <st data-num=\"02005\" class=\"\">about to</st> <st data-num=\"07971\" class=\"\">send</st> my <st data-num=\"04397\" class=\"\">messenger</st>,<n id=\"1\" /> who will <st data-num=\"06437\" class=\"\">clear</st> the <st data-num=\"01870\" class=\"\">way</st> <st data-num=\"06440\" class=\"\">before</st> me. Indeed, the <st data-num=\"0136 0834\">Lord</st><n id=\"2\" /> <st data-num=\"0859\" class=\"\">you</st> are <st data-num=\"01245\" class=\"\">seeking</st> will <st data-num=\"06597\" class=\"\">suddenly</st> <st data-num=\"0935\" class=\"\">come</st> <st data-num=\"0413\" class=\"\">to</st> his <st data-num=\"01964\" class=\"\">temple</st>, and the <st data-num=\"04397\" class=\"\">messenger</st><n id=\"3\" /> of the <st data-num=\"01285\" class=\"\">covenant</st>, <st data-num=\"0834\" class=\"\">whom</st> <st data-num=\"0859\" class=\"\">you</st> <st data-num=\"02655\" class=\"\">long for</st>, is <st data-num=\"02009\" class=\"\">certainly</st> <st data-num=\"0935\" class=\"\">coming</st>,\u201d <st data-num=\"0559\" class=\"\">says</st> the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span> of <st data-num=\"06635\" class=\"\">Heaven\u2019s Armies</st>. </p>",
    "verse": "1"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Malachi",
    "chapter": "3",
    "text": "<p class=\"bodytext\"><st data-num=\"04310\" class=\"\">Who</st> can <st data-num=\"03557\" class=\"\">endure</st> the <st data-num=\"03117\" class=\"\">day</st> of his <st data-num=\"0935\" class=\"\">coming</st>? <st data-num=\"04310\" class=\"\">Who</st> can keep <st data-num=\"05975\" class=\"\">standing</st> when he <st data-num=\"07200\" class=\"\">appears</st>? <st data-num=\"03588\" class=\"\">For</st> <st data-num=\"01931\" class=\"\">he</st> will be like a <st data-num=\"06884\" class=\"\">refiner\u2019s</st> <st data-num=\"0784\" class=\"\">fire</st>,<n id=\"1\" /> like a <st data-num=\"03526\" class=\"\">launderer\u2019s</st> <st data-num=\"01287\" class=\"\">soap</st>. ",
    "verse": "2"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Malachi",
    "chapter": "3",
    "text": "He will <st data-num=\"03427\" class=\"\">act like</st> a <st data-num=\"06884\" class=\"\">refiner</st> and <st data-num=\"02891\" class=\"\">purifier</st> of <st data-num=\"03701\" class=\"\">silver</st> and will <st data-num=\"02891\" class=\"\">cleanse</st> the <st data-num=\"01121 03878\">Levites</st> and <st data-num=\"02212\" class=\"\">refine</st> them like <st data-num=\"02091\" class=\"\">gold</st> and <st data-num=\"03701\" class=\"\">silver</st>. Then they <st data-num=\"01961\" class=\"\">will</st> <st data-num=\"05066\" class=\"\">offer</st> the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span> a <st data-num=\"06666\" class=\"\">proper</st> <st data-num=\"04503\" class=\"\">offering</st>. ",
    "verse": "3"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Malachi",
    "chapter": "3",
    "text": "The <st data-num=\"04503\" class=\"\">offerings</st><n id=\"1\" /> of <st data-num=\"03063\" class=\"\">Judah</st> and <st data-num=\"03389\" class=\"\">Jerusalem</st><n id=\"2\" /> will <st data-num=\"06149\" class=\"\">be pleasing</st> to the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span> as in <st data-num=\"05769\" class=\"\">former</st> <st data-num=\"03117\" class=\"\">times</st> and <st data-num=\"08141\" class=\"\">years</st> <st data-num=\"06931\" class=\"\">past</st>. </p>",
    "verse": "4"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Malachi",
    "chapter": "3",
    "text": "<p class=\"bodytext\">\u201cI<n id=\"1\" /> will <st data-num=\"07126\" class=\"\">come</st> <st data-num=\"0413\" class=\"\">to</st> you in <st data-num=\"04941\" class=\"\">judgment</st>. I will <st data-num=\"01961\" class=\"\">be</st> <st data-num=\"04116\" class=\"\">quick</st> to <st data-num=\"05707\" class=\"\">testify</st> against those who <st data-num=\"03784\" class=\"\">practice divination</st>; those who <st data-num=\"05003\" class=\"\">commit adultery</st>; those who <st data-num=\"08267\" class=\"\">break</st> <st data-num=\"07650\" class=\"\">promises</st>;<n id=\"2\" /> and those who <st data-num=\"06231 07939\">exploit</st> <st data-num=\"07916\" class=\"\">workers</st>, <st data-num=\"0490\" class=\"\">widows</st>, and <st data-num=\"03490\" class=\"\">orphans</st>,<n id=\"3\" /> who <st data-num=\"05186\" class=\"\">refuse to help</st><n id=\"4\" /> the <st data-num=\"01616\" class=\"\">resident foreigner</st><n id=\"5\" /> and in this way show they do <st data-num=\"03808\" class=\"\">not</st> <st data-num=\"03372\" class=\"\">fear</st> me,\u201d <st data-num=\"0559\" class=\"\">says</st> the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span> of <st data-num=\"06635\" class=\"\">Heaven\u2019s Armies</st>. </p>",
    "verse": "5"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Malachi",
    "chapter": "3",
    "text": "<p class=\"bodytext\">\u201c<st data-num=\"03588\" class=\"\">Since</st>, <st data-num=\"0589\" class=\"\">I</st>, the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span>, do <st data-num=\"03808\" class=\"\">not</st> <st data-num=\"08138\" class=\"\">go back on</st> my <st data-num=\"08138\" class=\"\">promises</st>,<n id=\"1\" /> <st data-num=\"0859\" class=\"\">you</st>, <st data-num=\"01121\" class=\"\">sons</st> of <st data-num=\"03290\" class=\"\">Jacob</st>, have <st data-num=\"03808\" class=\"\">not</st> <st data-num=\"03615\" class=\"\">perished</st>. ",
    "verse": "6"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Malachi",
    "chapter": "3",
    "text": "From the <st data-num=\"03117\" class=\"\">days</st> of your <st data-num=\"01\" class=\"\">ancestors</st> you have <st data-num=\"05493\" class=\"\">ignored</st><n id=\"1\" /> my <st data-num=\"02706\" class=\"\">commandments</st><n id=\"2\" /> and have <st data-num=\"03808\" class=\"\">not</st> <st data-num=\"08104\" class=\"\">kept</st> them. <st data-num=\"07725\" class=\"\">Return</st> <st data-num=\"0413\" class=\"\">to</st> me, and I will <st data-num=\"07725\" class=\"\">return</st> <st data-num=\"0413\" class=\"\">to</st> you,\u201d <st data-num=\"0559\" class=\"\">says</st> the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span> of <st data-num=\"06635\" class=\"\">Heaven\u2019s Armies</st>. \u201cBut you <st data-num=\"0559\" class=\"\">say</st>, \u2018<st data-num=\"04100\" class=\"\">How</st> should we <st data-num=\"07725\" class=\"\">return</st>?\u2019 ",
    "verse": "7"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Malachi",
    "chapter": "3",
    "text": "Can a <st data-num=\"0120\" class=\"\">person</st> <st data-num=\"06906\" class=\"\">rob</st><n id=\"1\" /> <st data-num=\"0430\" class=\"\">God</st>? <st data-num=\"0859\" class=\"\">You</st> are <st data-num=\"03588\" class=\"\">indeed</st> <st data-num=\"06906\" class=\"\">robbing</st> me, but you <st data-num=\"0559\" class=\"\">say</st>, \u2018<st data-num=\"04100\" class=\"\">How</st> are we <st data-num=\"06906\" class=\"\">robbing</st> you?\u2019 In <st data-num=\"04643\" class=\"\">tithes</st> and <st data-num=\"08641\" class=\"\">contributions</st>!<n id=\"2\" /> ",
    "verse": "8"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Malachi",
    "chapter": "3",
    "text": "<st data-num=\"0859\" class=\"\">You</st> are <st data-num=\"0779\" class=\"\">bound</st> for <st data-num=\"03994\" class=\"\">judgment</st><n id=\"1\" /> because <st data-num=\"0859\" class=\"\">you</st> are <st data-num=\"06906\" class=\"\">robbing</st> me\u2014this <st data-num=\"03605\" class=\"\">whole</st> <st data-num=\"01471\" class=\"\">nation</st> is guilty.<n id=\"2\" /></p>",
    "verse": "9"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Malachi",
    "chapter": "3",
    "text": "<p class=\"bodytext\">\u201c<st data-num=\"0935\" class=\"\">Bring</st> the <st data-num=\"03605\" class=\"\">entire</st> <st data-num=\"04643\" class=\"\">tithe</st> <st data-num=\"0413\" class=\"\">into</st> the <st data-num=\"01004 0214\">storehouse</st><n id=\"1\" /> so that there may <st data-num=\"01961\" class=\"\">be</st> <st data-num=\"02964\" class=\"\">food</st> in my <st data-num=\"01004\" class=\"\">temple</st>. <st data-num=\"0974 04994\">Test</st> me in <st data-num=\"02063\" class=\"\">this matter</st>,\u201d <st data-num=\"0559\" class=\"\">says</st> the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span> of <st data-num=\"06635\" class=\"\">Heaven\u2019s Armies</st>, \u201cto see <st data-num=\"0518\" class=\"\">if</st> I will <st data-num=\"03808\" class=\"\">not</st> <st data-num=\"06605\" class=\"\">open</st> for you the <st data-num=\"0699\" class=\"\">windows</st> of <st data-num=\"08064\" class=\"\">heaven</st> and <st data-num=\"07324\" class=\"\">pour out</st> <st data-num=\"01293\" class=\"\">blessing</st> for you <st data-num=\"05704\" class=\"\">until</st> there is <st data-num=\"01097\" class=\"\">no</st> <st data-num=\"01767\" class=\"\">room for it all</st>. ",
    "verse": "10"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Malachi",
    "chapter": "3",
    "text": "Then I will <st data-num=\"01605\" class=\"\">stop</st> the <st data-num=\"0398\" class=\"\">plague</st><n id=\"1\" /> <st data-num=\"03808\" class=\"\">from</st> <st data-num=\"07843\" class=\"\">ruining</st> your <st data-num=\"06529 0127\">crops</st>,<n id=\"2\" /> and the <st data-num=\"01612\" class=\"\">vine</st> will <st data-num=\"03808\" class=\"\">not</st> <st data-num=\"07921\" class=\"\">lose</st> its <st data-num=\"07921\" class=\"\">fruit</st> <st data-num=\"07704\" class=\"\">before harvest</st>,\u201d <st data-num=\"0559\" class=\"\">says</st> the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span> of <st data-num=\"06635\" class=\"\">Heaven\u2019s Armies</st>. ",
    "verse": "11"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Malachi",
    "chapter": "3",
    "text": "\u201c<st data-num=\"03605\" class=\"\">All</st> <st data-num=\"01471\" class=\"\">nations</st> will <st data-num=\"0833\" class=\"\">call</st> you <st data-num=\"0833\" class=\"\">blessed</st>, <st data-num=\"03588\" class=\"\">for</st> <st data-num=\"0859\" class=\"\">you</st> indeed will <st data-num=\"01961\" class=\"\">live in</st><n id=\"1\" /> a <st data-num=\"02656\" class=\"\">delightful</st> <st data-num=\"0776\" class=\"\">land</st>,\u201d <st data-num=\"0559\" class=\"\">says</st> the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span> of <st data-num=\"06635\" class=\"\">Heaven\u2019s Armies</st>. </p>",
    "verse": "12"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Malachi",
    "chapter": "3",
    "text": "<p class=\"bodytext\">\u201c<st data-num=\"01697\" class=\"\">You</st> have <st data-num=\"02388 05921\">criticized</st> me <st data-num=\"02388 05921\">sharply</st>,\u201d<n id=\"1\" /> <st data-num=\"0559\" class=\"\">says</st> the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span>, \u201cbut you <st data-num=\"0559\" class=\"\">ask</st>, \u2018<st data-num=\"04100\" class=\"\">How</st> have we <st data-num=\"01696 05921\">criticized</st> you?\u2019",
    "verse": "13"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Malachi",
    "chapter": "3",
    "text": "You have <st data-num=\"0559\" class=\"\">said</st>, \u2018It is <st data-num=\"07723\" class=\"\">useless</st> to <st data-num=\"05647\" class=\"\">serve</st> <st data-num=\"0430\" class=\"\">God</st>. <st data-num=\"04100\" class=\"\">How</st> have we been <st data-num=\"01215\" class=\"\">helped</st><n id=\"1\" /> <st data-num=\"03588\" class=\"\">by</st> <st data-num=\"08104\" class=\"\">keeping</st> his <st data-num=\"04931\" class=\"\">requirements</st> and <st data-num=\"01980\" class=\"\">going about</st> like <st data-num=\"06941\" class=\"\">mourners</st> <st data-num=\"06440\" class=\"\">before</st> the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span> of <st data-num=\"06635\" class=\"\">Heaven\u2019s Armies</st>?<n id=\"2\" /> ",
    "verse": "14"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Malachi",
    "chapter": "3",
    "text": "So <st data-num=\"06258\" class=\"\">now</st> <st data-num=\"0587\" class=\"\">we</st> <st data-num=\"0833\" class=\"\">consider</st> the <st data-num=\"02086\" class=\"\">arrogant</st> <st data-num=\"0833\" class=\"\">to be blessed</st>; <st data-num=\"01571\" class=\"\">indeed</st>, those who <st data-num=\"06213\" class=\"\">practice</st> <st data-num=\"07564\" class=\"\">evil</st> are <st data-num=\"01129\" class=\"\">successful</st>.<n id=\"1\" /> <st data-num=\"01571\" class=\"\">In fact</st>, those who <st data-num=\"0974\" class=\"\">challenge</st><n id=\"2\" /> <st data-num=\"0430\" class=\"\">God</st> <st data-num=\"04422\" class=\"\">escape</st>!\u2019\u201d </p>",
    "verse": "15"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Malachi",
    "chapter": "3",
    "text": "<p class=\"bodytext\"><st data-num=\"0227\" class=\"\">Then</st> those who <st data-num=\"03372\" class=\"\">respected</st><n id=\"1\" /> the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span> <st data-num=\"01696\" class=\"\">spoke</st> to <st data-num=\"0376\" class=\"\">one</st> <st data-num=\"07453\" class=\"\">another</st>, and the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span> <st data-num=\"07181 08085\">took notice</st>.<n id=\"2\" /> A <st data-num=\"05612\" class=\"\">scroll</st><n id=\"3\" /> was <st data-num=\"03789\" class=\"\">prepared</st> <st data-num=\"06440\" class=\"\">before</st> him in which were <st data-num=\"02146\" class=\"\">recorded</st> the names of those who <st data-num=\"03372\" class=\"\">respected</st> the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span> and <st data-num=\"02803\" class=\"\">honored</st> his <st data-num=\"08034\" class=\"\">name</st>. ",
    "verse": "16"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Malachi",
    "chapter": "3",
    "text": "\u201cThey will <st data-num=\"01961\" class=\"\">belong</st> to me,\u201d <st data-num=\"0559\" class=\"\">says</st> the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span> of <st data-num=\"06635\" class=\"\">Heaven\u2019s Armies</st>, \u201cin the <st data-num=\"03117\" class=\"\">day</st> <st data-num=\"0834\" class=\"\">when</st> <st data-num=\"0589\" class=\"\">I</st> <st data-num=\"06213\" class=\"\">prepare</st> my <st data-num=\"05459\" class=\"\">own special property</st>.<n id=\"1\" /> I will <st data-num=\"02550 05921\">spare</st> them <st data-num=\"0834\" class=\"\">as</st> a <st data-num=\"0376\" class=\"\">man</st> <st data-num=\"02550 05921\">spares</st> his <st data-num=\"01121\" class=\"\">son</st> who <st data-num=\"05647\" class=\"\">serves</st> him.",
    "verse": "17"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Malachi",
    "chapter": "3",
    "text": "Then <st data-num=\"07725\" class=\"\">once more</st> you will <st data-num=\"07200\" class=\"\">see</st> that I make a <st data-num=\"0996\" class=\"\">distinction between</st><n id=\"1\" /> the <st data-num=\"06662\" class=\"\">righteous</st> and the <st data-num=\"07563\" class=\"\">wicked</st>, <st data-num=\"0996\" class=\"\">between</st> the one who <st data-num=\"05647\" class=\"\">serves</st> <st data-num=\"0430\" class=\"\">God</st> and the one <st data-num=\"0834\" class=\"\">who</st> <st data-num=\"05647\" class=\"\">does</st> <st data-num=\"03808\" class=\"\">not</st>. </p>",
    "verse": "18"
  }
]